-- U.K.'s Takeover Panel Issues First `Cold Shoulder' Decision in 18 Years
-- Erik Larson
-- 2010-07-14T09:28:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-14/u-k-s-takeover-panel-dismisses-appeal-of-investors-who-bought-pcit-shares.html

          
          
             The U.K. Takeover Panel issued a so-
called cold shoulder decision against three investors accused of
skirting rules when they acquired 6.7 million shares of
Principle Capital Investment Trust Plc.  
